      • getCharset

        public java.lang.String getCharset()
        从接口复制的说明: ContentDescriptor

        The body descriptors character set, defaulted appropriately for the MIME type.

        For TEXT types, this will be defaulted to UTF-8. For other types, when the charset parameter is missing this property will be null.

        返回:
        Character set, which has been parsed from the content-type definition. Not null for TEXT types, when unset will be set to default UTF-8. For other types, when unset, null will be returned.

      • getTransferEncoding

        public java.lang.String getTransferEncoding()
        从接口复制的说明: ContentDescriptor
        Returns the body descriptors transfer encoding.
        返回:
        The transfer encoding. Must not be null, but "7bit", if no transfer-encoding was specified.

      • getContentLength

        public long getContentLength()
        从接口复制的说明: ContentDescriptor
        Returns the body descriptors content-length.
        返回:
        Content length, if known, or -1, to indicate the absence of a content-length header.
